text.section:
The Fund consists of:
Moneys made available from an assessment on equine feed as required under § 6-107.2 of this article;
Moneys made available to the Fund by general, federal, or special fund appropriations;
Moneys made available to the Fund by gifts, grants or transfers from any government or unit or instrumentality of a government or from any private sector sources; and
Moneys made available from licensing and inspection of horse stables as required under §§ 2-711, 2-712, and 2-713 of this subtitle.
